| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5142 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a2da14c4-44ff-58b1-904a-c3e2a65f166b"
